data.meta_description: Danish-Norwegian Monarch. He is remembered as the ruling monarch of the Kingdoms of Denmark and Norway from 1699 to 1730. During his reign, Denmark and Norway were at war with Sweden from 1709 to 1720; this war was called the Great Nordic War or Great Northern War. As a result of the war, Denmark gained the territory...
